cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper deals with visual pattern recognition using machine learning methods, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and Artificial Immune System Principles (AIS). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of small data sets, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of AIS principles suggests that it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
